      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FinTech_AuthVault项目画一个Git流程图，展示从main分支cherry-pick特定提交到develop分支的场景。标题就叫\"Cherry-pick from main (FinTech_AuthVault)\"吧。",
